<HEADLINE>
CANDIDATES SLING MUD IN MICHIGAN 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service
 clients)  
 RESENDING TO INSERT TIME ELEMENT IN LEDE 
 By KRIS MAYES  
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic  
