</P>
<P>
   A3049 BC-NY-REPUBS-NYT 231 22:41 U P
</P>
<P>
   NEW YORK LAWMAKER SWITCHES TO MCCAIN
</P>
<P>
   A3041 BC-MICH-VOTERS-1STLD-WRITETHRU-970(2TAKES)-NYT 1022 22:31
U P
</P>
