<P>
   TEXAS-EXECUTE (Gatesvill, Texas) -- As Texas prepares for its
second execution of a woman, on Feb. 24, there is none of the
hoopla that surrounded the first execution two years ago. But
supporters of Betty Lou Beets believe that years of abuse at the
hands of her husband should spare her from death. By Lynda Gorov.
1700 words.
</P>
