</P>
<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL &LR;  (``i'' code)
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-TAIWAN (Dateline to kum) _ China issued a new white paper
Monday reiterating its policy on Taiwan calling for peaceful
reunification under the ``One Country, Two Systems'' formula
through negotiation. But in a toughening of its position, the paper
also warned for the first time it would take ``all drastic measures
possible, including the use of force,'' if Taiwan repeatedly
rebuffed the peaceful overtures. China had previously only refused
to rule out using military muscle to bring the island back under
mainland rule in case of three scenarios _ a foreign invasion, a
proclamation of independence or ``internal chaos.'' By Erik
Eckholm.
</P>
<P>
   With
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-TAIWAN-U.S. (Washington) _ React on Beijing paper. Could
fold into China. By Jane Perlez.
</P>
<P>
