<P>
   CRESTED BUTTE-COLORADO _ Crested Butte Mountain Resort is know
for its rough terrain skiing. The U.S. Extreme Freesking
Championships have been held there for the past three years.
</P>
<P>
   IRWIN-COLORADO _ The largest snowcat skiing resort in North
America is in Irwin, Colo. Located 12 miles from Crested Butte.
</P>
