<HEADLINE>
DOCTORS LEARN FROM STAGE'S `WIT'
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: This story also moved on the ``e'' entertainment wire. 
By EVAN HENERSON 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
