avoidable allergen or irritant. By Jane E. Brody. (1150 words)
</P>
<P>
   SCI-VITAL-SIGNS (Undated) _ News and notes on health and
nutrition:
</P>
<P>
   _ Scientists in Italy have found new support for the hypothesis
that the increased incidence of allergies and infectious disease
