   ``Sogno,'' Andrea Bocelli
</P>
<P>
   ``Livin' La Vida Loca,'' Ricky Martin
</P>
<P>
   ``Brand New Day,'' Sting
</P>
<P>
   And the winner will be: Andrea Bocelli. Every Grammy voter has
probably eaten in an Italian restaurant this year, so they've heard
this song. Ricky Martin could very well walk away with this one,
but I can't see it going to any of the other three.
</P>
<P>
   BEST FEMALE R&AMP;B VOCAL PERFORMANCE
</P>
