   ``Do Something,'' Macy Gray
</P>
<P>
   ``It's Not Right But It's Okay,'' Whitney
</P>
<P>
   Houston
</P>
<P>
   And the winner will be: Whitney Houston. Blige is the best of
this bunch, but Grammy voters tend to stick with the old faves.
</P>
<P>
   BEST MALE R&AMP;B VOCAL PERFORMANCE
</P>
