   ``Smooth,'' Itaal Shur &AMP; Rob Thomas, songwriters (Santana
Featuring Rob Thomas)
</P>
<P>
   ``Unpretty,'' Dallas Austin &AMP; Tionne ``T-Boz'' Watkins,
songwriters (TLC)
</P>
