   (Shania Twain)
</P>
<P>
   And the winner will be: ``Smooth.'' The best thing about
``Smooth'' is the guitar, not the composition. But when it rains it
pours on Grammy night and this will clearly be the night of
Santana's golden armload. Shania also has a good chance because
she's been passed over in this category the past two years.
</P>
