</P>
<P>
   And the winner will be: TLC. Critically acclaimed and
multiplatinum: a can't-miss combo.
</P>
<P>
   BEST RAP ALBUM
</P>
<P>
   ``E.L.E. (Extinction Level Event - The Final World Front),''
Busta Rhymes
</P>
