   ``I Am,'' Nas
</P>
<P>
   ``Things Fall Apart,'' The Roots
</P>
<P>
   And the winner will be: Will Smith. OK, that's a Chris Rock
joke. I can't see Eminem winning, because the Grammy electorate
rarely awards artists who are being sued by their mothers. The
Roots and Nas will split the ``rap as an art form'' vote and Busta
Rhymes is, well, he's Busta Rhymes. Let's go with Missy Elliott.
</P>
<P>
   BEST FEMALE COUNTRY VOCAL PERFORMANCE
