   ``Man! I Feel Like A Woman!'' Shania Twain
</P>
<P>
   And the winner will be: Shania Twain. Harris and Krauss are
Grammy pets and McBride won this category at the CMA awards, but
Shania's just got too much sales power to ignore.
</P>
<P>
   BEST MALE COUNTRY VOCAL PERFORMANCE
</P>
<P>
   ``Don't Come Cryin' To Me,'' Vince Gill
</P>
