</P>
<P>
   And the winner will be: George Jones. This award could really go
to any of the five, which is why I'll give the nod to the legend.
Plus it would be a good chance to show up the rival CMA awards,
which snubbed Jones a few months back by not allowing him enough
time to sing the entire song
</P>
<P>
   BEST COUNTRY ALBUM
