<TEXT>
<P>
   The following Arizona Republic story has been added for use by
clients of the NYTimes News Service for  &UR; TUES., FEB 21. If you have
any questions, please contact the Republic News Desk at (602)
444-8286.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &UR; INHERITING-2 (undated) _ The second part of  &UR; INHERITING THE
WORLD, &UR; an in-depth analysis of American foreign policy options at
the opening of the century and millennium. This part of the series
focuses on Republican thinking. Special for The Arizona Republic by
NORMAN LEVINE. Story will move in the ``A'' and ``K'' categories.
</P>
