<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-21 22:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4023 &Cx1f; tad-z
u s BC-BBN-REDS-OPENER22-COX     02-21 0454
